      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_3_00016"/><hi rend="latintype">Hrn. Dr. Rich. Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb213" type="place">Ischl</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb41463" type="place">Schulgasse 8</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_3_00017"/>Lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>ich ka<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> heute leider nicht zu Ihnen <pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_3_00018"/>ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en.</p><p>Grüß<unclear>en</unclear> Sie <hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Loris</rs></hi>.</p><p>We<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> ich aber <hi rend="underline" n="1">doch</hi> ka<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c> ich er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t nach
               zehn.</p><p>Unwahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinlich.</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
